    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>The Act 2 barrow-draugr are third-tier undead — calcified bone forms wrapped in tattered leather, risen from the ancient Bone-Fields rather than fresh cairns. They move with jerking, unnatural gaits and radiate bitter cold. Their Bone-Shatter Strike deals devastating blows, while their Calcified Grasp can restrain heroes in place with icy claws. These draugr are spawned by the Bone-Singer through its Arise ability, flooding the battlefield in expanding numbers.</p>",
